What's in this version:
1. Move all strings to github, with acknowledgement to all the translators. Fork and send pull requests to help translate VPlayer.
2. Use different colors in video list item, to indicate watched videos.
3. Use smoother thumbnails loading in video list.
4. Can take snapshot when using hardware decoding in Android 4.1+ .
5. Fix hardware decoding issues for some devices with Android 4.1+ .
6. Fix SeekBar and CheckBox style bugs for Android 4.2.

